objects.name: Hint1
objects.string: Drag wires into place to complete the circuit! Use WASD to move the electricity towards the receptacle.

content.text: Drag wires into place to complete the circuit! Use WASD to move the electricity towards the receptacle.

objects.name: Hint2
objects.string: You may have to pick up items you used before to make a path to the end!

content.text: You may have to pick up items you used before to make a path to the end!

objects.name: Hint3
objects.string: You can route power to doors to open them! You can only access items inside of rooms you are in. Walk with the arrow keys.

content.text: You can route power to doors to open them! You can only access items inside of rooms you are in. Walk with the arrow keys.

objects.string: You can only pick up wires in rooms you are located in!

objects.name: Story_Starter
objects.string:
You recently graduated in electrical engineering with a passion for fixing things. With a toolbox full of knowledge and a heart full of ambition, you decide to pursue your dream of starting a small business. 

You set up shop in your own neighborhood, offering to fix electrical appliances and fixtures in people's homes. 

Are you ready to enter your first challenge?

content.text:
You recently graduated in electrical engineering with a passion for fixing things. With a toolbox full of knowledge and a heart full of ambition, you decide to pursue your dream of starting a small business. 

You set up shop in your own neighborhood, offering to fix electrical appliances and fixtures in people's homes. 

Are you ready to enter your first challenge?
